Package org.digidoc4j.impl.asic

Class AsicCompositeContainerValidationResult

java.lang.Object
org.digidoc4j.impl.asic.AsicCompositeContainerValidationResult
All Implemented Interfaces:
ContainerValidationResult, SignatureValidationResult, ValidationResult
public class AsicCompositeContainerValidationResult extends Object implements ContainerValidationResult
A composite validation result that aggregates the contents of both an arbitrary nested container and a nesting ASiC container.
